OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FHundreds of people have died in India,
OL,7,FPakistan and Nepal after cloudbursts
OL,8,Foccurred, causing flash flooding with
OL,9,Flittle warning.
OL,11,FIn northwestern Pakistan, as many as
OL,12,F300 people died in the district of
OL,13,FBuner following a cloudburst. The
OL,14,Fstrength and volume of rain triggered
OL,15,Fflash flooding, landslides, mudflows,
OL,16,Fand boulders to fall from steep
OL,17,Fslopes, flattening homes and reducing
OL,18,Fvillages to rubble.
