OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FPakistani officials said a warning to
OL,7,Fallow evacuations was not possible, as
OL,8,Fthe cloudburst struck before residents
OL,9,Fcould be alerted.
OL,11,FAnother cloudburst in the Indian-
OL,12,Fadministered region of Kashmir killed
OL,13,Fat least 60 people and left more than
OL,14,F200 missing. The flash floods struck
OL,15,Fon Thursday during an annual Hindu
OL,16,Fpilgrimage to the area, causing
OL,17,Fthousands to be evacuated.
OL,19,FSince monsoons began in June, at least
OL,20,F41 people have died and another 121
OL,21,Fpeople have been injured in Nepal.
