OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FThe northern Indian state of
OL,7,FUttarakhand had a cloudburst earlier
OL,8,Fthis month. Extraordinary footage
OL,9,Fshowed floodwaters surging down a
OL,10,Fmountain and crashing into a village.
OL,11,FFour people died.
OL,13,FBut what are cloudbursts and why are
OL,14,Fthey causing so much chaos in these
OL,15,Fcountries?
OL,17,FWhat is a cloudburst?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
