OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FA cloudburst occurs when a large
OL,7,Fvolume of rain falls in a very short
OL,8,Fperiod of time, usually more than 10cm
OL,9,Fwithin an hour over a localised area,
OL,10,Faround 30 square kilometres.
OL,12,FThey are sudden and violent, dropping
OL,13,Fthe equivalent of several hours of
OL,14,Fnormal rainfall. The event is the
OL,15,Fbursting of a cloud and the discharge
OL,16,Fof its contents at the same time, like
OL,17,Fa rain bomb.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
