OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FThe instantaneous falling of water can
OL,7,Ftrigger deadly floods, as the area it
OL,8,Flands on struggles to deal with the
OL,9,Fimpact of so much water, so suddenly.
OL,11,FCloudbursts occur when warm, moist air
OL,12,Frises rapidly and condenses into heavy
OL,13,Frain clouds.
OL,15,FMountainous areas are more susceptible
OL,16,Fto forming cloudbursts, as air is
OL,17,Fforced to rise after encountering a
OL,18,Fhill or mountain. The rising air will
OL,19,Fcool and condense to form heavy
OL,20,Frainclouds.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
