OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FThe hills or mountains can act as
OL,7,Fbarriers and trap clouds, preventing
OL,8,Fthem from dispersing or moving easily.
OL,9,FStrong upward currents keep moisture
OL,10,Fsuspended inside the clouds,
OL,11,Fpreventing rainfall.
OL,13,FWhen the clouds cannot hold the
OL,14,Faccumulated moisture anymore, they
OL,15,Fburst and release it all at once.
OL,17,FShocking footage shows the moment a
OL,18,Fcloudburst-induced flash flood surges
OL,19,Fdown a mountain in Northern India, and
OL,20,Fcrashes into a village in early
OL,21,FAugust. Ellie Pitt reports.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
