OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FWhy do they particularly affect India
OL,7,Fand Pakistan?
OL,9,FCloudbursts thrive in moisture,
OL,10,Fmonsoons and mountains. Some regions
OL,11,Fof India and Pakistan have all three,
OL,12,Fmaking them particularly vulnerable to
OL,13,Fthese extreme weather events.
OL,15,FThe Himalayas, Karakoram and Hindu
OL,16,FKush mountain ranges are home to the
OL,17,Fworld's highest and most famous peaks,
OL,18,Fspanning multiple countries, including
OL,19,FIndia and Pakistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
