OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FGlobal warming is making it worse. A
OL,7,Fwarmer air mass can hold more
OL,8,Fmoisture, creating the ideal
OL,9,Fconditions for sudden and intense
OL,10,Fdownpours. Both India and Pakistan
OL,11,Fhave seen cloudbursts happening more
OL,12,Ffrequently.
OL,14,FIn 2013, 6,000 people died in
OL,15,FUttarakhand when a cloudburst struck,
OL,16,Fmaking it one of the deadliest natural
OL,17,Fdisasters India has seen this century.
OL,19,FWhy were residents in Pakistan not
OL,20,Fwarned?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
