OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FIt's difficult to predict cloudbursts
OL,7,Fbecause of their size, duration,
OL,8,Fsuddenness and complex atmospheric
OL,9,Fmechanisms.
OL,11,FA Pakistani official said there was
OL,12,F"no forecasting system anywhere in the
OL,13,Fworld" that could predict the exact
OL,14,Ftime and location of a cloudburst.
OL,16,FThe Pakistani government said that
OL,17,Fwhile an early warning system was in
OL,18,Fplace, the downpour was so sudden that
OL,19,Fit struck before residents could be
OL,20,Falerted.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
