OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FPrecautions are possible. Residents in
OL,7,Fsusceptible areas are advised not to
OL,8,Fbuild homes next to rivers and
OL,9,Fvalleys, to postpone travel to hilly
OL,10,Fareas if rain is forecast, and to keep
OL,11,Fan emergency kit ready.
OL,13,FPlanting trees can also reduce surface
OL,14,Frunoff and enhance water absorption,
OL,15,Falongside regular clearing and
OL,16,Fwidening of riverbanks and drainage
OL,17,Fchannels.
OL,19,FHow does climate change affect
OL,20,Fcloudbursts?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
