OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FExperts say cloudbursts have increased
OL,7,Fin frequency in recent years, partly
OL,8,Fdue to climate change.
OL,10,FThe damage they wreak has also
OL,11,Fincreased due to unplanned development
OL,12,Fin mountain areas.
OL,14,FFor every 1C rise, the air can hold
OL,15,F7% more moisture, increasing the
OL,16,Fpotential for heavy rainfall.
