OL,3,CWhat are cloudbursts? The deadly
OL,4,Cweather event in India and Pakistan
OL,6,FThe warming of the Indian Ocean and
OL,7,FArabian Sea pushes more moisture into
OL,8,Fthe atmosphere around Pakistan and
OL,9,FIndia, while melting glaciers and snow
OL,10,Falter local weather patterns, making
OL,11,Frainfall events more erratic and
OL,12,Fextreme.
OL,14,FUrbanisation in the form of
OL,15,Fdeforestation and wetland loss reduces
OL,16,Fthe land's ability to absorb water.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
